Employee Assistance Program Sometimes we all need someone to talk to. Employees and their immediate family members are able to access professional and 100% confidential counselling, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. You can get help for personal issues like relationship difficulties, grief and loss, finance matters or for workplace issues like bullying, harassment or dealing with change.
No one needs to know that you have used the service and no personal information is released back to Sydney Trains or NSW TrainLink. Just call the below number to book a face to face or telephone session.
